			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Most people agree that mages need a few changes to bring us up to par of other classes. Most want dps increase especially in the form of pets. Unfortunately soe seems reluctant to add dps from pets or nukes. I think a good way to implement dps would be through fixing or replacing some of our broken aaxps.
<br />
 
<br />
 
<br />
Fix
<br />
FB~ it needs a 9 min recast and last 1 min.to be effective.
<br />
ele agility~it is broken and needs to be fixed
<br />
pet crit and pet flurry~needs to be increased dps
<br />
MGB(fix to work well with DS or replace)
<br />
 
<br />
Remove
<br />
Turned summoned
<br />
hastened banish
<br />
 
<br />
Add(names are generic)
<br />
Host of water (just like HOE with no push)
<br />
Host of air  (just like hoe with slightly less damage no push and moor stun proc)
<br />
host of fire (same amount of pets that stand back and nuke like SOR)
<br />
host mastery (must have all host aaxps max to take)(1 of each elemental 25 dps each last 1 min)
<br />
 
<br />
(all must have separate timers to be effective)
<br />
 
<br />
This is just a suggestion as a way to add badly needed dps and give us some actual aaxps worth taking. This would help make us once again master of pets and at the same time not be stepping on any other class’s toes.
<br />
 
<br />
 
<br />
Just an idea
<br />
Mariuss</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
