<br />

<br />
At max level I have parsed it doing a combined 100 dps(once all are spawned and attacking) on level 65ish Ferubi mobs from the back, and about 85dps on same mobs from the front.
<br />

<br />
Overall it outdamages our pet swarm (since it lasts twice as long) and they dont die as fast (plus can enrage which is extremely handy).
<br />

<br />
I have seen first hand a single shaman swarm hold up a Time Vallon Zek doppleganger for at least 30 seconds by themselves with enrages. (I know since it was my shaman alt that did it).
<br />

<br />
HoE is a decent ability, but it could certainly use a bit of a buffing when a priest classes' swarm outperforms ours in pretty much every respect.  At least we have appx the same re-use timer as shamans do now.
<br />

